              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9574214504861350115">A sweet fun read for younger girls. I read this to my daughters 15 and twin 13 year olds and they liked it. It is a retelling of Cinderella but it is very different. They gave the story a fun twist and it is a great read. The ending is a little silly but fun. My girls loved that everyone got there happy ending. I would say for 12 and up. There is a really bad guy and things get a little dicey for our main character and there is some violence, but overall very clean.</span>

