              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5010314813276830244">Lucinda is an unfortunate and rather silly 15-year-old orphan. When her uncle dies, his hateful widow turns the girl out penniless into the streets. Various unlikely things happen, including a good witch, a prince, prison, a ball, and a goat. Implausible but cute.</span>

          </span>
